docs.text: Welcome to Otus-SRE This project is for study purpose only. Usage After clone run "vagrant up" and you will get working development enviroment based on bento/ubuntu-18.04 Then "vagrant ssh" and run "python ./code/flask-sqlite3-todo-crud/app.py" Versions Hypervisor - Oracle VM VirtualBox VM Runner v6.1.32 Vagrant - Vagrant 2.2.19 Folders and Ports ./code >> /home/vagrant/code # Vagrant synced folder ./code # Code folder so new code may be placed there ./code/flask-sqlite3-todo-crud/ # Application is located here 5000 # Application uses port 5000, forwarded to port 5000 on host https://github.com/renat-nizamov/flask-sqlite3-todo-crud # Application source
